data.description: Welcome to 813 Pebble Ln, your beautiful 4 bed, 2 bath, 1.55 acre swim spa oasis. Upon entering the property you are greeted by the large driveway with ample parking space and a chain link fence great for all your fury friends! Through the front door you will walk directly into the large living room. Next to the dining room enjoy a spacious eat-in kitchen equipped with appliances. This home also features 4 roomy bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with a shower and soaking tub, and an adorable home office ideal for working from home! Step through the back door and walk directly into the large deck area perfect for Grilling and family gatherings. Wish you could have a spa day everyday? Now you can! The back deck is accompanied by an extraordinarily relaxing temperature controlled swim spa. The large backyard contains marvelous blueberry bushes and an additional L shaped concrete parking space with a 30 amp electric hookup for a camper/ RV. This property also features a large basement and full electric outdoor shed so storage is never an issue! Welcome home!
